根据下面的公式，分析 RL 为什么训推不一致: \begin{equation}
    \theta \leftarrow \theta+\mu \cdot \mathbb{E}_{\underbrace{a \sim \pi(\theta)}_{\text{rollout}}}[R(a) \cdot \underbrace{\nabla_\theta \log \pi(a, \theta)}_{\text{training}}].
\end{equation}

then explain Truncated Importance Sampling (TIS):
\begin{equation}
    \mathbb{E}_{a \sim \pi_{\mathrm{vllm}}(\theta)}\left[
    \min(\frac{\pi_{\mathrm{fsdp}}(a, \theta)}{\pi_{\mathrm{vllm}}(a, \theta)}, C) \cdot R(a) \cdot \nabla_\theta \log \pi_{\mathrm{fsdp}}(a, \theta)\right].
\end{equation}
